 [Packaging]
 - Now shipping as "Spark", formerly shipped as "Spark::Form"
 - Bugs/Issues now go to Github Issues
 - Repository now hosted under the "perl-spark" organisation.
 - Some urls SSL-ified.
 - Now ignores anything in attic/ ( Check git if you want this dir )

